companyName: First Trust Small Cap US Equity Select ETF
description:
The investment seeks investment results that correspond generally to the price and yield (before the fund's fees and expenses) of an equity index called the Nasdaq Riskalyze US Small Cap Index (the "index").
 The fund will normally invest at least 90% of its net assets (including investment borrowings) in common stocks that comprise the index. The index is designed to select dividend-paying US small capitalization securities that are included in the Nasdaq US 700 Small Cap Index (the "base index"). The fund is non-diversified.
